text: Piotr Olszewski (born 25 April 1973) is a Polish rower. He competed in the men's coxless four event at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Poland Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Warsaw
